Type: Package
Package: episensr
Title: Basic Sensitivity Analysis of Epidemiological Results
Version: 1.3.0
Date: 2023-08-29
Authors@R:
    person("Denis", "Haine", , "denis.haine@proton.me", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6691-7335"))
Description: Basic sensitivity analysis of the observed relative risks
    adjusting for unmeasured confounding and misclassification of the
    exposure/outcome, or both. It follows the bias analysis methods and
    examples from the book by Lash T.L, Fox M.P, and Fink A.K.  "Applying
    Quantitative Bias Analysis to Epidemiologic Data", ('Springer', 2021).
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/dhaine/episensr,
    https://dhaine.github.io/episensr/
BugReports: https://github.com/dhaine/episensr/issues
